PERCYJACKSON-INCOMING_WAVE.description:
Raise the [gold]Tide[/gold] by {Tide:diff()}.
Deal damage equal to {Mult:plural:|{Mult:diff()} x }the new [gold]Tide[/gold].{InCombat:
(Deals {CalculatedDamage:diff()} damage)}

PERCYJACKSON-HIGH_TIDE.description:
Raise the maximum [gold]Tide[/gold] and [gold]Tide[/gold] by {Tide:diff()}.
Deal damage equal to {Mult:diff()} times the maximum [gold]Tide[/gold].{InCombat:
(Deals {CalculatedDamage:diff()} damage)}

PERCYJACKSON-SURFING_LESSONS.description:
Deal damage equal to the [gold]Tide[/gold] gained this turn.
Raise the [gold]Tide[/gold] by the unblocked damage dealt.{InCombat:
(Deals {CalculatedDamage:diff()} damage)}

PERCYJACKSON-WAVE_AFTER_WAVE.description:
Add {Cards:diff()} [gold]Water[/gold] to your [gold]Hand[/gold].
Deal {Damage:diff()} damage to ALL enemies a number of times equal to the cards in your [gold]Hand[/gold].{InCombat:
(Hits {HitCount:diff()} time{HitCount:plural:|s})}

PERCYJACKSON-TSUNAMI.description:
Exhaust ALL [gold]Unplayable[/gold] cards.
Deal {Damage:diff()} damage for each [gold]Unplayable[/gold] card in your [gold]Exhaust Pile[/gold].{InCombat:
(Hits {HitCount:diff()} time{HitCount:plural:|s})}
